data.description: Beautiful Home in a Quiet Community at the End of the Court. This Open Concept Floor Plan offers an Eat in Kitchen with New Granite Counters and Newer Stainless Steel Appliances.  Spacious Light filled Living Room with adjoining Dining Area. Sliding Glass Door Leads to the Private, Fully Fenced Back Yard that Backs to Trees and Open Space. Three Generous sized Bedrooms and Upgraded Primary Bathroom are located upstairs. Roof, HVAC System and Water Heater all less than 3 Years old! Dale City Recreation Center is right around the corner. Home is Close to Shops, Restaurants and Transportation!
